article.description: — Christiaan Jones had 20 points as Stetson topped Kennesaw State 74-61 on Friday night.
article.headline: Jones scores 20 to carry Stetson past Kennesaw State 74-61
article.linkText: Jones scores 20 to carry Stetson past Kennesaw State 74-61
article.story: KENNESAW, Ga. -- — Christiaan Jones had 20 points as Stetson topped Kennesaw State 74-61 on Friday night. Chase Johnston had 17 points for Stetson (8-10, 5-6 Atlantic Sun Conference). Rob Perry added 13 points. Mahamadou Diawara had 12 points and 10 rebounds. Spencer Rodgers had 17 points for the Owls (3-16, 0-11), who have now lost 14 games in a row. Terrell Burden added 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
